\c 67
\s Abantu bonke kabamdumise uNkulunkulu
\d Kumqondisi wokuhlabelela. Ngamachacho. Isihlabelelo, ingoma
\p
\v 1 Nkulunkulu, woba lomusa kithi usibusise\x + Nani 6.25,24.\x*, ukhanyise ubuso bakho phezu kwethu. \w Sela\w**\x + Nani 6.25. Jobe 33.26. Hlab. 4.6. 31.16.\x*.
\v 2 Ukuze indlela yakho yaziwe emhlabeni, usindiso lwakho ezizweni zonke\x + Luka 2.30,31. Tit. 2.11.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Kazikudumise izizwe, Nkulunkulu, kabakudumise abantu bonke\x + 67.5. Hlab. 66.4.\x*.
\v 4 Izizwe kazijabule zihlabele ngentokozo, ngoba uzabahlulela abantu ngokuqonda, uhole izizwe emhlabeni. \w Sela\w**\x + Hlab. 58.11.\x*.
\v 5 Kazikudumise izizwe, Nkulunkulu, kabakudumise abantu bonke\x + 67.5. Hlab. 66.4.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Umhlaba uzathela izithelo zawo; uNkulunkulu, uNkulunkulu wethu uzasibusisa\x + Hlab. 85.12. Levi 26.4.\x*.
\v 7 UNkulunkulu uzasibusisa, layo yonke imikhawulo yomhlaba izamesaba\x + Hlab. 22.27.\x*.
